data.description: This five bedrooms two bath two story home is located on a large lot on the western side of Quincy in the Western Heights Community.  Home boast large living area and family room, oversized kitchen, inside laundry, hardwood floors and high ceilings throughout the home, front porch, side and rear decks, inground pool, oversized shed and partial fence. Make this your home today with some TLC.
